atlas_to_fs5.Rd

Maps average parcellation surface values (e.g. produced with the fs5_to_atlas() function) to the fsaverage5 space

Usage

atlas_to_fs5(parcel_data)

Arguments

parcel_data

A matrix object containing average surface measures for each region of interest, see the fs5_to_atlas() output format.

Value

A matrix object containing vertex-wise surface data mapped in fsaverage5 space

Details

The function currently works with the Desikan-Killiany-70, Schaefer-100, Schaefer-200, Glasser-360, or Destrieux-148 atlases. ROI to vertex mapping data for 1 to 4 were obtained from the enigma toolbox ; and data for 5 from nilearn.datasets.fetch_atlas_surf_destrieux . atlas_to_fs5() will automatically detect the atlas based on the number of columns.
